window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>We call them the grays. For years, they lurked in shadows. For years, they struck from the dark. Kidnapping us. Torturing us. Studying us. </p> <p>Now they unleash their full fury. </p> <p>Thousands of their saucers attack Earth. Our armies crumble. Earth burns. </p> <p>Yet from the fire, heroes rise. Marco Emery. Addy Linden. Einav Ben-Ari. Names everyone on Earth knows. The names of legends. Names now whispered as a prayer. </p> <p>Around the heroes, humanity will rally. Under their leadership, we will fight. Together we can win. </p> <p>The grays think us weak. But we will stand strong! </p>"; 
